sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Platform as Platform Ingress<br/>(KServe / Gateway API /<br/>kube-rbac-proxy)
    participant Runtime as Caikit Runtime<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant LocalMod as Local Module<br/>(TextGeneration /<br/>EmbeddingModule)
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(in-memory GPU/CPU)
    participant TGISMod as TGIS Module<br/>(TextGenerationTGIS /<br/>PeftPromptTuningTGIS)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>gRPC (configurable port)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 1: Local Text Generation / Embedding Inference
    Client->>Platform: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    Platform->>Runtime: Forward request<br/>HTTP :8080 or gRPC :8085
    Runtime->>LocalMod: Python in-process call
    LocalMod->>HFModel: PyTorch inference
    HFModel-->>LocalMod: Generated text / embeddings
    LocalMod-->>Runtime: Response
    Runtime-->>Platform: Response
    Platform-->>Client: JSON / gRPC Response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: TGIS Remote Text Generation
    Client->>Platform: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    Platform->>Runtime: Forward request
    Runtime->>TGISMod: Python in-process call
    TGISMod->>TGIS: gRPC generation request<br/>TLS (optional) / mTLS (optional)
    TGIS-->>TGISMod: Generated text (streaming supported)
    TGISMod-->>Runtime: Response
    Runtime-->>Platform: Response
    Platform-->>Client: JSON / gRPC Response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: Prompt Tuning Training
    Client->>Platform: POST train API<br/>Auth: Platform-managed
    Platform->>Runtime: Forward request
    Runtime->>LocalMod: PeftPromptTuning.train()
    LocalMod->>HFModel: PyTorch training<br/>(gradient accumulation,<br/>mixed precision via Accelerate)
    HFModel-->>LocalMod: Training complete
    LocalMod-->>LocalMod: Save prompt vectors<br/>(encoder.pt / decoder.pt)
    LocalMod-->>Runtime: Trained model reference
    Runtime-->>Platform: Response
    Platform-->>Client: Training complete

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 4: Model Download (optional)
    Runtime->>HFHub: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Token auth (optional)
    HFHub-->>Runtime: Model weights & tokenizer
